// Template-local markdownlint-cli2 config. markdownlint-cli2 walks up from
// each linted file's directory and merges the closest `.markdownlint-cli2.*`
// it finds; `ignores` in a per-directory config filter files whose
// `dirInfo.dir` matches this directory, so placing the config INSIDE the
// templates directory is what actually skips these files (a config one level
// higher merges its options but wouldn't match the file's relative path).
//
// The record templates carry deliberate fill-in placeholders (<title>,
// <Option A>, <pro>…) that markdownlint misreads as inline HTML (MD033); real
// records have no placeholders, so records/ stays linted. oxfmt still formats
// the templates.
{
	"$schema": "../../../../.schemas/markdownlint-cli2.json",
	"ignores": ["*"],
}
